Place them in your class8.java below another previously added item.

Save compile, and run your client, log in.
When you have logged in, make sure your models you downloaded are placed in your models folder, then type this:

[code]add model 14090
add model 14091
add model 14092[/code]

And so on all up to 14103 i think?

